## Invariants (never break these)

- `useFleetSocket` is the ONLY place fleet state lives on frontend вЂ” no component fetches independently
- All API routes filter by `CURRENT_OPERATOR_ID` вЂ” no unscoped queries
- `tokens.js` is the ONLY place colors are defined вЂ” import everywhere else
- `docker compose down && up` produces clean working state
- `VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN` missing в†’ render error state, don't crash silently
- Simulator publishes identical Redis format whether `DEMO_MODE=true` or false

